{"tid":1340602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗今晚一個警察都無！","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:20:04.000Z","uid":209337,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89127c6e142b656a064b04bd737e9b1a6c1fcf65","tid":1340602,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:37.000Z","msg":"成晚，白衫黑幫一早已經係10點幾打人<br />\n到左11點仲要上埋西鐵站打市民<br />\n<br />\n我睇live 睇到立場姐姐比人打，仲要有好多市民講，佢老婆比人打<br />\n到白衫走曬，就立即出現警察！直行直過<br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講警察都係打份工！唔好再同我講咩都唔關林鄭事！<br />\n唔好再同我講做咩好死死知人會打人都入去元朗！<br />\n<br />\n#我表妹係架西鐵度返朗屏，喊到仆街<br />\n#我老婆比人打到爆曬血<br />\n#立場姐姐都隻手都畀相信係棍棒嘅物體打咗一兩分鐘，電話都飛咗出嚟幾次<br />\n#diu 警察 而家警察唔幫巿民？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭，想玩香港人玩到幾時！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6zq8Xw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6zq8Xw.png&h=64d41fa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bf0c64bb1f7c15e57d87e57d17d074a1829f584","tid":1340602,"uid":75582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"交稅做咩！？？？？？？<br />\n養班冇用既人？？警黑合作/？？？"},{"pid":"1dc21a0893ad75cbabed843d2d31e4d016f73f20","tid":1340602,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"老百姓殺死黑社會不犯法<br />\n<br />\n【警方通報&ldquo;昆山砍人案&rdquo;：騎車男不負刑事責任 撤銷該案】<br />\n<br />\n江蘇昆山，寶馬男追砍電動車主遭反殺引發熱議。今日，昆山公安通報稱：電動車主於海明的行為屬於正當防衛，不負刑事責任，公安機關依法撤銷於海明案件。拍手叫好！！"},{"pid":"ca4942e8d257a7d01b6a2225d4bf4c862652b528","tid":1340602,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到屋企嘅手足入黎!! 有地方落腳!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3b506a00d0a88eddcca8daed936dc3d3e058cc","tid":1340602,"uid":267822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"響應罷工罷市罷課呀屌！！！<br />\n白衫人見市民出街胡亂打人！！！！<br />\n警賊唔lun理㗎啦！！！！！<br />\n文宣做野呀呀呀呀呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"0d26d13a47270177c3cea7701d2e6c843c8af990","tid":1340602,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求：</span></strong><br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士、撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會、並追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>追究元朗暴徒行兇、警察失蹤</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7397e81f854ff4fe5ab453ca507259eca943a107","tid":1340602,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"成立獨立調查委員會"},{"pid":"09dd7f0335f79923c9a54fda7ee14c491fa14b5d","tid":1340602,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0a3813333a519bc044dc2ba1e0c8c5ed31c53750","tid":1340602,"uid":279763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7397e81f854ff4fe5ab453ca507259eca943a107","tid":1340602,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"成立獨立調查委員會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"下？政府冇左架啦！<br />\n係就自己成立武裝自衛隊！<br />\n同政府講，同自己去篤自己灰有咩分別？"},{"pid":"72817c2b5f890a1d7bcf6f30b0e8c6813a967500","tid":1340602,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"西鐵一個保安都無！"},{"pid":"e67754442e9a2fcb3da274277fb16bb776b43099","tid":1340602,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"王威信唔知去左邊！"}]}